{"tid":492553,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺愈返得耐工人愈蠢？","createTime":"2017-12-07T15:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T15:33:50.000Z","uid":96485,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8d5d954153173ac376504f4d8304ddec28c6d5c2","tid":492553,"uid":96485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:54:30.000Z","msg":"唔計專處理突發事件嘅工<br />\n日日做埋啲手板眼見嘅工夫<br />\n愈做愈覺得個人嘅思考能力，記性都下降<br />\n<br />\n可以做啲咩keep住自己個腦日日轉下，唔駛愈嚟愈蠢？"},{"pid":"3819c80cf0492e6e3a88a6c9f51c9c9d508f7440","tid":492553,"uid":42064,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔計專處理突發事件嘅工<br />\n日日做埋啲手板眼見嘅工夫<br />\n愈做愈覺得個人嘅思考能力，記性都下降<br />\n<br />\n可以做啲咩keep住自己個腦日日轉下，唔駛愈嚟愈蠢？</blockquote><br />\n其實唔關突唔突發，返普通工係會令你個諗嘢方法死板左。<br />\n而返用腦嘅工，係令你嚴倦思考，因為平時已經太用腦。<br />\n<br />\n所以認真工作係點都會蠢"},{"pid":"2ae62c54d7a8940d0c05f18292f277e9791f42b0","tid":492553,"uid":96485,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔計專處理突發事件嘅工<br />\n日日做埋啲手板眼見嘅工夫<br />\n愈做愈覺得個人嘅思考能力，記性都下降<br />\n<br />\n可以做啲咩keep住自己個腦日日轉下，唔駛愈嚟愈蠢？</blockquote><br />\n其實唔關突唔突發，返普通工係會令你個諗嘢方法死板左。<br />\n而返用腦嘅工，係令你嚴倦思考，因為平時已經太用腦。<br />\n<br />\n所以認真工作係點都會蠢</blockquote><br />\n所言甚是<br />\n同事醒目啲嗰批都係做嘢麻麻地<br />\n其實自己心底好想好似佢地咁醒，但一做嘢自己就會認真咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d005ac495ad8cec822729b8e75df099d0be1ab91","tid":492553,"uid":42064,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔計專處理突發事件嘅工<br />\n日日做埋啲手板眼見嘅工夫<br />\n愈做愈覺得個人嘅思考能力，記性都下降<br />\n<br />\n可以做啲咩keep住自己個腦日日轉下，唔駛愈嚟愈蠢？</blockquote><br />\n其實唔關突唔突發，返普通工係會令你個諗嘢方法死板左。<br />\n而返用腦嘅工，係令你嚴倦思考，因為平時已經太用腦。<br />\n<br />\n所以認真工作係點都會蠢</blockquote><br />\n所言甚是<br />\n同事醒目啲嗰批都係做嘢麻麻地<br />\n其實自己心底好想好似佢地咁醒，但一做嘢自己就會認真咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n保留返精神俾自己放工用最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507b55103e773363e30e0b81c0c4f4ba9353bb67","tid":492553,"uid":39866,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:45:35.000Z","msg":"成日都有新野新問題要迫自己學<br />\n個人會變到長期都好大壓力好燥底"},{"pid":"8ecb4f63b6b1da3e30e0079542a6fcc1299aeef5","tid":492553,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:04:11.000Z","msg":"你都識講你日日做埋啲手板眼見嘅工夫<br />\n<br />\n轉工/放工後學嘢啦"},{"pid":"91a45905851d172eae27f97d8f3faca220fdf188","tid":492553,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日都有新野新問題要迫自己學<br />\n個人會變到長期都好大壓力好燥底</blockquote><br />\n係，日日都突然，個人會好辛苦"},{"pid":"8537ae7c80466163336def6f3616e531042838e6","tid":492553,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日都有新野新問題要迫自己學<br />\n個人會變到長期都好大壓力好燥底</blockquote><br />\n係，日日都突然，個人會好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n突發"},{"pid":"ebead3635a327df191cd1e17f44dab8a0e6c45bf","tid":492553,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:11:19.000Z","msg":"辭職了"},{"pid":"2d6144b164562a155ed940fbc361b3e865241aad","tid":492553,"uid":96485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都識講你日日做埋啲手板眼見嘅工夫<br />\n<br />\n轉工/放工後學嘢啦</blockquote><br />\n人工title升得快，養到屋企人<br />\n又未搵到人生目標<br />\n騎牛搵馬住先<br />\n<br />\n所以有時都幾佩服為興趣去搵工嘅人"},{"pid":"636688cf914fa4bb78cd6b5de82f0c496fede238","tid":492553,"uid":96485,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日都有新野新問題要迫自己學<br />\n個人會變到長期都好大壓力好燥底</blockquote><br />\n轉壓力轉化成力量<br />\n話畀自己知，學到新嘢又可以贏人一條街，對升職加人工有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d060ce2626a432dfd61bd44c5f27d2de992c1c2","tid":492553,"uid":96485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:39:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辭職了</blockquote><br />\n巴打有咩計劃？"},{"pid":"5fbb6b487f033f3e6da2c1a271c74fee2bd9c279","tid":492553,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6312179adc3fa93bda7baf681ffb50f089941af1","tid":492553,"uid":2671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"翻左份新工三個月，每日都有新野學要記，仲好似咩都唔識咁，仲未學得曬好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a378bb43c1aa81f0508f13b3bd9f6958ad9cfc35","tid":492553,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T13:56:15.000Z","msg":"每日返工都做下數獨，可以用下個腦"},{"pid":"65884c042f9c9fe7ace05b59145aa6d97c8fdfae","tid":492553,"uid":96485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翻左份新工三個月，每日都有新野學要記，仲好似咩都唔識咁，仲未學得曬好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未適應到姐，三個月只係好短時間<br />\n我都用咗一年去適應人際關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n適應咗就得心應手㗎喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9716eed77d44b57a6ff74c1e1e90271df6334286","tid":492553,"uid":96485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日返工都做下數獨，可以用下個腦</blockquote><br />\n我有時間玩數獨就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc843245eec79037ca2d7afb41e831f87a4cad7a","tid":492553,"uid":117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T17:00:14.000Z","msg":"報d course讀下書囉"},{"pid":"263d69c562a20ef4190274ebefc38dfe3c567fa6","tid":492553,"uid":96485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報d course讀下書囉</blockquote><br />\n有諗過，諗住考吓一世受用嘅牌"},{"pid":"4e1db435d6ff4d006f04c59a591fae2f56700855","tid":492553,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日返工都做下數獨，可以用下個腦</blockquote><br />\n睇完你講之後搵左個數獨黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02c73fce12906ca4c085525f37d62f0d5027fff","tid":492553,"uid":164419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2be4bf0eaad308d3cbd732590b49f0010fe341c","tid":492553,"uid":96485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f02c73fce12906ca4c085525f37d62f0d5027fff","tid":492553,"uid":164419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:07:25.000Z","msg":"又返工了！feel到個人又準備退化了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc527482774522b4fb90047210679a413ed93d0","tid":492553,"uid":90839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"Exact7ly 呢幾日都係咁諗呢個問題 呢份工唔算有壓力 得閒時可以由朝早坐到收工 但覺得人地努力學緊野時自己就頹廢緊 好似原地踏步冇進步過 但好驚轉工果種不安同忙到冇左自己嘅生活 有時係度諗究竟係返工返到好撚忙長進到好多skills 定日日冇事做但係放工後充實自己比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4331f1187416eeb6908b68e3b67125580d9424","tid":492553,"uid":24642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afc527482774522b4fb90047210679a413ed93d0","tid":492553,"uid":90839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"Exact7ly 呢幾日都係咁諗呢個問題 呢份工唔算有壓力 得閒時可以由朝早坐到收工 但覺得人地努力學緊野時自己就頹廢緊 好似原地踏步冇進步過 但好驚轉工果種不安同忙到冇左自己嘅生活 有時係度諗究竟係返工返到好撚忙長進到好多skills 定日日冇事做但係放工後充實自己比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過類似問題<br />\n結論都係有份輕鬆啲嘅工<br />\n放工後充實自己  我覺得會有彈性啲<br />\n但要確定自己有實行力、有恆心先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係就好易霉<br />\n（講到自己有選擇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"42a7cc1df7d5f2e55061cb3b52b9abf056e6d7b4","tid":492553,"uid":96485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3b4331f1187416eeb6908b68e3b67125580d9424","tid":492553,"uid":24642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afc527482774522b4fb90047210679a413ed93d0","tid":492553,"uid":90839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"Exact7ly 呢幾日都係咁諗呢個問題 呢份工唔算有壓力 得閒時可以由朝早坐到收工 但覺得人地努力學緊野時自己就頹廢緊 好似原地踏步冇進步過 但好驚轉工果種不安同忙到冇左自己嘅生活 有時係度諗究竟係返工返到好撚忙長進到好多skills 定日日冇事做但係放工後充實自己比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過類似問題<br />\n結論都係有份輕鬆啲嘅工<br />\n放工後充實自己  我覺得會有彈性啲<br />\n但要確定自己有實行力、有恆心先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係就好易霉<br />\n（講到自己有選擇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"大家都stuck咗喺comfort zone入面<br />\n我會咁諗：如果覺得自己老咗之後唔會後悔嘅，咁就去做，而家會有想改變嘅念頭，因為自己覺得自己值得更好<br />\n所以有勇氣跳出comfort zone好重要"}]}